#: urpm/cli/main.py:1232
msgid ""
"Add a media source.\n"
"\n"
"For official Mageia media, just provide the URL:\n"
"  urpm media add https://mirrors.mageia.org/mageia/9/x86_64/media/core/"
"release/\n"
"\n"
"For custom/third-party media, use --custom with name and short_name:\n"
"  urpm media add --custom \"My Repo\" myrepo https://example.com/repo/"
"x86_64/\n"
"\n"
"For legacy mode (non-Mageia URL with explicit name):\n"
"  urpm media add --name \"My Media\" https://example.com/repo/\n"
msgstr ""
"Eine Medienquelle hinzufügen.\n"
"\n"
"Für offizielle Mageia-Medien genügt die Angabe der URL:\n"
"  urpm media add https://mirrors.mageia.org/mageia/9/x86_64/media/core/"
"release/\n"
"\n"
"Für benutzerdefinierte Medien/Drittanbieter-Medien --custom mit Name und Kurzname verwenden:\n"
"  urpm media add --custom \"Mein Repo\" meinrepo https://example.com/repo/"
"x86_64/\n"
"\n"
"Für den Legacy-Modus (Nicht-Mageia-URL mit explizitem Namen):\n"
"  urpm media add --name \"Meine Medien\" https://example.com/repo/\n"

#: urpm/cli/main.py:1244
msgid "Media URL"
msgstr "Medien-URL"

#: urpm/cli/main.py:1247
